    "type": "VerificationActivity",
    "name": "Mesh Independence Study for CFD Hemolysis Model",
    "description": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted across three mesh densities (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 5.8M cells, fine: 14.3M cells) to assess discretization error in predicted hemolysis index and velocity field. Richardson extrapolation applied to estimate grid convergence index (GCI) for the relative hemolysis index QoI at all five CPB operating points.",
    "activityType": "MeshConvergenceVerification"
  },
