    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 12% of experimental measurements across all CPB operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
